#: data/org.gnome.shell.gschema.xml.in:312
#: data/org.gnome.shell.gschema.xml.in:339
msgid "Limit switcher to current workspace."
msgstr "Finwetha skwycheller dhe vordh a-lemmyn."

#: data/org.gnome.shell.gschema.xml.in:313
msgid ""
"If true, only applications that have windows on the current workspace are "
"shown in the switcher. Otherwise, all applications are included."
msgstr ""
"Mar gwir, appys gans fenestri war'n bordh a-lemmyn hepken yw diskwedhys y'n "
"skwycheller. Yn ken maner, oll appys yw synsys."

#: data/org.gnome.shell.gschema.xml.in:330
msgid "The application icon mode."
msgstr "An fordh arwodhik app."

#: data/org.gnome.shell.gschema.xml.in:331
msgid ""
"Configures how the windows are shown in the switcher. Valid possibilities "
"are “thumbnail-only” (shows a thumbnail of the window), “app-icon-only” "
"(shows only the application icon) or “both”."
msgstr ""
"Selya fatel an fenestri yw diskwedhys y'n skwycheller. Galladewderyow ewn yw "
"“thumbnail-only” (diskwedhes skeusennik a'n fenester), “app-icon-only” "
"(diskwedhes an arwodhik app hepken) or “both” (an dhew)."

#: data/org.gnome.shell.gschema.xml.in:340
msgid ""
"If true, only windows from the current workspace are shown in the switcher. "
"Otherwise, all windows are included."
msgstr ""
"Mar kwir, fenestri dhyworth an bordh a-lemmyn hepken yw diskwedhys y'n "
"skwycheller. Yn ken maner, oll fenestri yw synsys."

